#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn3.17"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn3.17:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.17:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. Childless "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn3.17:0.3"
msgid "17. Appamādasutta "
msgstr "17. Diligence "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.195, sc1
msgctxt "sn3.17:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.17:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn3.17:1.3"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho rājā pasenadi kosalo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Seated to one side, King Pasenadi said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn3.17:1.4"
msgid "“atthi nu kho, bhante, eko dhammo yo ubho atthe samadhiggayha tiṭṭhati—"
msgstr "“Sir, is there one thing that secures benefits for both "

msgctxt "sn3.17:1.5"
msgid "diṭṭhadhammikañceva atthaṃ samparāyikañcā”ti? "
msgstr "the present life and lives to come?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn3.17:2.1"
msgid "“Atthi kho, mahārāja, eko dhammo yo ubho atthe samadhiggayha tiṭṭhati—"
msgstr "“There is, great king.” "

msgctxt "sn3.17:2.2"
msgid "diṭṭhadhammikañceva atthaṃ samparāyikañcā”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn3.17:3.1"
msgid "“Katamo pana, bhante, eko dhammo, yo ubho atthe samadhiggayha tiṭṭhati—"
msgstr "“So what is it?” "

msgctxt "sn3.17:3.2"
msgid "diṭṭhadhammikañceva atthaṃ samparāyikañcā”ti? "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.87, pts2ed1.196, sc4
msgctxt "sn3.17:4.1"
msgid "“Appamādo kho, mahārāja, eko dhammo, yo ubho atthe samadhiggayha tiṭṭhati—"
msgstr "“Diligence, great king, is one thing that, when developed and cultivated, secures benefits for both "

msgctxt "sn3.17:4.2"
msgid "diṭṭhadhammikañceva atthaṃ samparāyikañcāti. "
msgstr "the present life and lives to come. "

#. VAR: jaṅgalānaṃ → jaṅgamānaṃ (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "sn3.17:4.3"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, yāni kānici jaṅgalānaṃ pāṇānaṃ padajātāni, sabbāni tāni hatthipade samodhānaṃ gacchanti, hatthipadaṃ tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati—yadidaṃ mahantattena; "
msgstr "The footprints of all creatures that walk can fit inside an elephant’s footprint. So an elephant’s footprint is said to be the biggest of them all. "

msgctxt "sn3.17:4.4"
msgid "evameva kho, mahārāja, appamādo eko dhammo, yo ubho atthe samadhiggayha tiṭṭhati—"
msgstr "In the same way, diligence is one thing that secures benefits for both "

msgctxt "sn3.17:4.5"
msgid "diṭṭhadhammikañceva atthaṃ samparāyikañcā”ti. "
msgstr "the present life and lives to come.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.17:4.6"
msgid "Idamavoca … pe … "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. … "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn3.17:5.1"
msgid "“Āyuṃ arogiyaṃ vaṇṇaṃ, "
msgstr "“For one who desires a continuous flow "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:5.2"
msgid "saggaṃ uccākulīnataṃ; "
msgstr "of exceptional delights—"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:5.3"
msgid "Ratiyo patthayantena, "
msgstr "long life, beauty, and health, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:5.4"
msgid "uḷārā aparāparā. "
msgstr "heaven, and birth in an eminent family—"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn3.17:6.1"
msgid "Appamādaṃ pasaṃsanti, "
msgstr "the astute praise diligence "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:6.2"
msgid "puññakiriyāsu paṇḍitā; "
msgstr "in making merit. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:6.3"
msgid "Appamatto ubho atthe, "
msgstr "Being diligent, an astute person "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:6.4"
msgid "adhiggaṇhāti paṇḍito. "
msgstr "secures both benefits: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn3.17:7.1"
msgid "Diṭṭhe dhamme ca yo attho, "
msgstr "the benefit in this life, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:7.2"
msgid "yo cattho samparāyiko; "
msgstr "and in lives to come. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:7.3"
msgid "Atthābhisamayā dhīro, "
msgstr "A wise one, comprehending the meaning, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:7.4"
msgid "paṇḍitoti pavuccatī”ti. "
msgstr "is called ‘astute’.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
